high_descs: Go left and then right and turn right to face the table with bread and a tea kettle.
Pick the tomato up from the counter.
Go left and then left again to face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and pick up the tomato.
Go left and then left again to face the counter with the tea pot.
Put the tomato down on the counter to the right of the tea pot.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed tomato down on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the wall, then turn right and go straight, then turn right to face the end of the kitchen island.
Pick up the tomato on the kitchen island.
Turn left and go forward, then turn left to face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave, heat it up, then take it out.
Turn left and go forward, then turn left to face the kitchen island.
Put the tomato on the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the middle of island on the side facing the stove.
Pick up the red tomato between the yellow knife and the plastic bowl on the counter.
Turn around and go to the microwave on the counter on the right side of the stove.
Heat the red tomato in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and go back to the middle of the kitchen island.
Place the tomato on the right of the tea kettle and in front of the plastic bowl.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated tomato on the counter.
